                     <interp inst="t18410405-1044-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="housebreaking"></interp> breaking and entering the dwelling-house of <persName id="t18410405-name-340" type="victimName">
                        <interp inst="t18410405-name-340" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
