                        <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18410405-1044-offence-1 t18410405-geo-3"></join>St. Giles Without, Cripplegate</placeName>, and stealing therein 6 spoons, value 3<hi rend="italic">s</hi>. 6<hi rend="italic">d</hi>.; his property: to which</rs>
